 the principles of which\ncan be readily extended to arbitrary higher-spin theories.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 Jul 2017 18:00:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 5 Aug 2017 18:57:04 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 27 Sep 2017 17:00:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-04"}
