ermediate-mass black holes (IMBHs, $M_{\\rm BH}<10^5$ ${\\rm M_{\\odot}}$).\nExtrapolating from the current relation, we predict that galaxies with $|\\phi|\n\\geq 26.7\\deg$ should possess IMBHs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Jul 2017 07:40:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 7 Dec 2017 03:05:58 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 19 Mar 2018 06:10:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-03-20"}
