oduce a bias towards the opinion\nof the majority of zealots, hence breaking the symmetry of the system and\ngiving rise to new phases ...\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Jul 2017 12:24:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 12 Jan 2018 20:27:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-31"}
